1.title: Miss Peggy
1.plot: A sweet thoughtful Southern Gal that likes to come out and make nice when talking to random people she meets.

2.title: Miss Roxy
2.plot: An Italian New York, East Coast, Brooklyn chic, aka 'Foxy Roxy' that likes to come out and put things into perspective when Miss Jadie gets too nice for her own good.

3.title: Miss Tessa
3.plot: A confident, straight to the point British gal that likes to come out often and talk to random British people as herself and always shares she lived in Kensington Gardens, London, England.

4.title: Miss Hawaiian Barbie
4.plot: The sweetest of The Jadie Bunch Show (2016), she gives a 'Barbie shout-out' to Miss Kristen Wiig for her adorable Saturday Night Live (1975) Barbie performance, we say 'good job from the Barbie Malibu Dream House and also in Hawaii'.

5.title: Miss Sadi Sadness
5.plot: While the quietest of The Jadie Bunch Show (2016), she has a beautiful place in 'Miss Jadie's' heart...'tears of sadness can also be joyful'. Inspired by the sweet character 'Sadness', from one of her favorite Disney Pixar Movies Inside Out (2015).

6.title: Miss Agent J.D.
6.plot: The most authoritative of The Jadie Bunch Show (2016) in this JIB Segment (Jadie in Black Segment), she gives a shout out to Mr Will Smith, Mr Tommy Lee Jones and the handsome ever Josh Brolin. Inspired by their Men in Black (1997) trilogy.

7.title: Miss Fatima De Fortune Teller
7.plot: The most clairvoyant and loudest of The Jadie Bunch Show (2016), in this 'Good Fortune Segment' she shares her thoughts on following your impulses, and how doing good onto others will bring good back into your life. She also does a 'Good Fortune' Reading for you with her globe, and sees good things coming your way.

8.title: Miss lil Mookey
8.plot: The monkey lover and cutest of The Jadie Bunch Show (2016), she shares how when Miss Jadie was little, she had to learn her 'r's and l's to pronounce correctly, and sounded like she was saying 'Ameo' instead of 'Amir' (which is her brothers name). Also shares Miss Jadie's lil monkey collection, that it's never to late to start doing what you love, and a fun tip to stay looking young.

9.title: Miss Shim Shay-rdasian
9.plot: One of the most known reality stars' on The Jadie Bunch Show (2016), her name protected for similarity and likeness, but she's a sweet person at heart doing good by sharing her appreciation for charity work, her love of being a mom and some fun things about 'Miss Jadie's' first impersonations of her.

10.title: Miss Nina Namaste
10.plot: The most centered and harmoniously loving of The Jadie Bunch Show (2016) she shares how to use the word 'Namaste' in your life when 'the shizzle hits the fan' (a chapter from Miss Jadie's upcoming book) and honors the light in you.

11.title: Miss Angry Alice
11.plot: The most vexed and annoyed of The Jadie Bunch Show (2016), she shares how opinions of others hold people back to do the things they really want to do, to accept others for their choices in life and how to move out of anger on the scale of emotions and find solutions in the things that are important to you. Inspired by the character 'Anger', from one of her favorite Disney Pixar Movies Inside Out (2015)

12.title: Miss Rae Ze Russian
12.plot: No she is not a spy, though the most serious and thankful for 'love' on The Jadie Bunch Show (2016). She shares a Love Story in this story telling segment, how Miss Jadie's hubby's grandpa, Sandor Stibinger, was a Freedom Fighter in the Hungarian Revolution during 1956, and escaped to America with her hubby's grandma Rose, his father, papa Gabor and his uncle Jon, that they had to hide in hay stacks and flee town to Austria to survive.

13.title: Miss Hawaiian Barbie~ Hokulea Voyaging Canoe
13.plot: The sweetest of The Jadie Bunch Show (2016) and the most requested back for a 2nd time on Season 1. She gives a shout out to a producer, Jeremy Allen, who she worked with on a project, for sharing the information on the Welcoming Ceremonies for the 3 Year Voyaging Canoe call the Hokulea, that traveled to NYC from Hawaii in 2016, and how we can help the Earth too by doing our part.

locations: New York City, New York, USA::(location)
imdb.plot outline: The Jadie Bunch Show (2016) is an original sketch-improv comedy show filled with a mix of all 'Miss Jadie's' characters played by Jade Elysan. Go on a fun journey of her accents, impersonations, fun, lighthearted views on life & inspiration for all. Based on her true life stories.
imdb.title: The Jadie Bunch Show
plot: _The Jadie Bunch Show_ (qv) (2016) is an original sketch-improv comedy show filled with a mix of all 'Miss Jadie's' characters played by 'Jade Elysan' (qv). Go on a fun journey of her accents, impersonations, fun, lighthearted views on life & inspiration for all. Based on her true life stories.::anonymous

Inspired by the opening credits of the 1969 original _The Brady Bunch (1969)_ (qv) show, this Uber Savvy Productions Original series, is the 1st known sketch-improv comedy show to use a similar opening credits design that _The Brady Bunch (1969)_ (qv) show is known for. This fun design (best viewed on Official Site Page) highlights short intro's for various 'Miss Characters' played by 'Jade Elysan' (qv), allowing the viewers to choose which 'Miss Character's' Full Episode they would like to view in order of their own viewing preference.::anonymous
